Package: ffTrack
Title: class for out-of-core GRanges based access for giant numeric genomic data tracks using ff package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Marcin Imielinski <mimielinski@nygenome.org>
Maintainer: Marcin Imielinski <mimielinski@nygenome.org>
Description: Allows building of objects of large genomically-indexed base-resolution sequence or numeric data for quasi-random out of memory access.   ffTrack objects are indexable using GRanges from GenomicRanges package.  Underlying files are written as .ffData objects using the ff package
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0),ff (>= 2.2), GenomicRanges (>= 1.18), rtracklayer (>= 1.25), gUtils (>= 0.1)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
